Sentencas: Nd0.6Sr0.4Co1-xCuxO3-delta (x = 0, 0.05, 0.1, 0.15, 0.2) (NSCCx) was prepared by replacing Co with Cu.

Titulo: Cu-doped Nd0.6Sr0.4Co1-xCuxO3-δ (x=0, 0.05, 0.1, 0.15, 0.2) as the cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
